710801f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 57th Street
710801f-a.text:
Twelfth Ave., south from West 57th Street. The area in the foreground,
is being cleared and made available for vehicular traffic.
May 21, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
